ActFall Economic Statement Implementation Act, 2022
SubjectOrder Fixing the Day on Which Certain Provisions of the Fall Economic Statement Implementation Act, 2022 Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing the day after the day on which this Order is made as the day on which sections 146, 147, 150 to 152, 157 and 158, subsections 159(2) and (3) and sections 160 and 166 of the FALL ECONOMIC STATEMENT IMPLEMENTATION ACT, 2022, chapter 19 of the Statutes of Canada, 2022, COME INTO FORCE in order to eliminate the interest accrual on Canada Student Loans and Canada Apprentice Loans.
